---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Tools" description="Current recommended resources and guides for Last War: Survival players, plus planned future calculators and tools.">
  <h1>Tools</h1>
  <p class="text-[#8a96b0]">Practical interactive tools for Last War: Survival.</p>

  <div class="mt-6">
    <a href="/resource-chest-calculator" class="block p-4 bg-[#1f2937] border border-[#374151] hover:border-[#60a5fa] rounded-xl transition-colors">
      <div class="font-semibold text-lg">Resource Chest Rewards Calculator</div>
      <div class="text-sm text-[#8a96b0] mt-1">Calculate total Gold (and other resources) from all your Resource Choice Chests and level-tied chests. Matches your current HQ level.</div>
      <div class="mt-2 text-xs text-[#60a5fa]">Try it now →</div>
    </a>
  </div>

  <h2 class="mt-8 text-lg font-semibold">More Tools Coming Soon</h2>
  <ul class="text-sm mt-2 space-y-1 text-[#8a96b0]">
    <li>Hero upgrade cost estimator</li>
    <li>Interactive squad builder</li>
    <li>Event & reminder tools</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="mt-8 text-xs text-[#6b7280]">
    All tools are designed to be accurate, mobile-friendly, and respect your current HQ level.
  </div>
</Layout>